    "description": "欢迎来到《<i>Stampede：Racing Royale</i>》——迄今最狂野的竞速赛事。你可以在惊心动魄的卡丁车赛车和对战赛事中猛踩油门，同时与多达60位参赛者同场竞技。善用技能和种类繁多的强化，你既能在经典的赛道赛中一马当先，也能在竞技场类对战中与众多对手一争高下，争夺最高得分。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >赛车大逃杀</h2><br>在《<i>Stampede: Racing Royale</i>》中，60名玩家将在共计三轮的淘汰赛事中捉对比拼，最终剩余两位选手争夺决赛冠军。各轮赛事中特别包括Stampede竞速赛，玩家要在创意指数达到凶残级的赛道上与最多59名其他对手展开经典卡丁车对抗，此外还有Stampede对战，参赛选手会被封锁在四处布满强化的竞技场中，唯有奋力争取胜利。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1851350/extras/d291cffe5de681bc0e0562366e645d79.poster.avif?t=1750080878\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1851350/extras/d291cffe5de681bc0e0562366e645d79.webm?t=1750080878\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1851350/extras/d291cffe5de681bc0e0562366e645d79.mp4?t=1750080878\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >收集与自定义</h2><br>持续参赛即可解锁新赛车和无穷无尽的自定义选项。找到你最喜爱的卡丁车，用自定义喷漆和贴纸把它打造成独一无二的那辆吧。另外还能给你的角色穿上最华丽的服装，确保你和赛车双双脱颖而出。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1851350/extras/48b8672c46eb48c341b2ac1ff02c51e7.poster.avif?t=1750080878\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1851350/extras/48b8672c46eb48c341b2ac1ff02c51e7.webm?t=1750080878\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1851350/extras/48b8672c46eb48c341b2ac1ff02c51e7.mp4?t=1750080878\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >7x24小时全天在线</h2><br>在Stampede的世界里，永远存在值得融入的事物——赛季、活动、挑战等游戏内容众多，这意味着你的比赛方式将不断变化，永远有新的奖励可以入手。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1851350/extras/0c862ebbf20517a6d2cd857fdbd837da.poster.avif?t=1750080878\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1851350/extras/0c862ebbf20517a6d2cd857fdbd837da.webm?t=1750080878\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1851350/extras/0c862ebbf20517a6d2cd857fdbd837da.mp4?t=1750080878\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >与好友一起比赛</h2><br>开始或加入派对，与朋友和家人一起体验《<i>Stampede: Racing Royale</i>》这款疯狂的动作佳作。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1851350/extras/f3e74ba7f2e40daf420a57faaeb4f3b4.poster.avif?t=1750080878\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1851350/extras/f3e74ba7f2e40daf420a57faaeb4f3b4.webm?t=1750080878\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1851350/extras/f3e74ba7f2e40daf420a57faaeb4f3b4.mp4?t=1750080878\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
